data.description: Step into this beautiful  5/3 home in Millcreek- Sugarmill to find an open floor plan with a kitchen that was fully remodeled in 2021 with granite countertops, shaker cabinets, stainless appliances, which include a range/oven with hood and an Alexa Refrigerator! Let's talk about the primary bathroom that was remodeled in 2019, it offers  natural marble dual vanities, walk-in closet, whirlpool bath, walk-in tile shower and bluetooth lights and vent fan. You will find the primary bedroom and ensuite downstairs  along with 2 guest bedrooms and a full bath. Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms and a full bath.  The home also provides a bonus room and a 2 car garage. The exterior of the home was painted in 2021 with weather shield paint and the yard is fully fenced for privacy. Move in ready for you to enjoy. $4,000 Painting Allowance toward new paint or Buyers closing costs with acceptable offer.
